    badge="Python | Pandas | Power BI"
  />
  <div class="divider my-0"></div>

  <HorizontalCard
    title="Sales Insights Data Analysis Project"
    img="/post_img.webp"
    desc="Designed SQL queries to extract and clean sales data (customers, transactions, revenue trends). Built revenue dashboards in Power BI using data modeling, DAX, and Power Query. Delivered actionable insights such as customer counts, market-specific performance, and revenue trends."
    url="#"
    badge="SQL | Power BI | DAX"
  />

  <HorizontalCard
    title="End-to-End Sales Insights Analysis"
    img="/post_img.webp"
    desc="SQL, Python, Pandas, Excel, Power BI, DAX Data Analytics. Orchestrated analytics workflow by integrating SQL, Python, Excel, and Power BI to extract and analyze sales data. Engineered robust pipelines using SQL and Python for data modeling, and leveraged Power BI dashboards for visualization. Delivered business insights simulating real-world decision-making scenarios."
    url="#"
